Makro is offering awesome deals in its Easter Sale, which will run until 26 March 2018 and features discounts on a wide range of products. The sale includes big discounts on electronics, gadgets, appliances, furniture, cameras, office equipment, and, of course, Easter eggs. Makro is also running South Africa’s biggest Easter egg hunt, with 72,000 eggs up for grabs and great prizes to be won. “Bring your kids in store,” said Makro, adding that the egg hunt is running until 2 April 2018. A selection of great tech deals from the Makro Easter Sale are shown below.      This article was published in partnership with Makro.